import axios from "axios" import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react' const Records = () => { const [student, setStudent] = useState({ id: null, firstname: null, lastname: null, phonenumber: null, zip: null, statecode: null, statename: null }) useEffect(() => { axios .post("http://localhost:3300/students", student) .then(() => alert(`Student ${$student.firstname} ${student.lastname} added successful.`)) .catch((err) => { alert("Error detected"); }); setStudent({ ...student }) }) return (






); }; export default Records
